:"园词根记忆：di（分开）+min(小)+ish→缩小"},{"type":"entry","text":"canny","headword":"canny"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 精明仔细的(shrewd and careful)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kaeni]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：can（能）+ny→能干的→精明仔细的"},{"type":"entry","text":"reiterate","headword":"reiterate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.重申，反复地说(to state over again or repeatedly)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ri'rtarert]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：re（反复）+iter（重申）+ate→重申，反复地说"},{"type":"text","text":"③] ingeminate, iterate"},{"type":"entry","text":"innate","headword":"innate"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.天生的，固有的(inborn, inbred)"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'nert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：in（进入）+nat（出生）+e→生来就带有的→天生的"},{"type":"text","text":"Unlike Sartre, who was born into a cultivated environment, receiving culture in"},{"type":"text","text":"his feeding bottle, so to speak, the child Camus had to fight to acquire a culture"},{"type":"text","text":"that was not innate."},{"type":"text","text":"connate, connatural, indigenous"},{"type":"entry","text":"rancor","headword":"rancor"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.深仇，怨恨(bitter deep-seated ill will; enmity)"},{"type":"text","text":"['raenkar]"},{"type":"text","text":"留 For someone suffering from stress, a holiday can act as a tonic, dispelling"},{"type":"text","text":"rancor, transforming indecision, and renewing the spirit."}]},{"number":67,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"doctrinaire","headword":"doctrinaire"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.教条主义者(one who attempts to put into effect an abstract doctrine) adj. 教条"},{"type":"text","text":"的，迁腐的（stubbornly adhering to a doctrine)"},{"type":"text","text":"[da:ktrr'ner]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自doctrine（n.教条）"},{"type":"text","text":"authoritarian, authoritative, dictatorial, dogmatic"},{"type":"entry","text":"flagrant","headword":"flagrant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.罪恶昭彰的：公然的(conspicuously offensive)"},{"type":"text","text":"['flergrant]"},{"type":"text","text":"不要和fragrant（adj.芳香的）相混"},{"type":"entry","text":"hypocrisy","headword":"hypocrisy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 伪善, 虚伪(a feigning to be what one is not or to believe what one does not)"},{"type":"text","text":"[hr'pa:krasi]"},{"type":"text","text":"cant, pecksniff, sanctimony, sham"},{"type":"text","text":"hypocritical (adj. 虚伪的)"},{"type":"entry","text":"accede","headword":"accede"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 同意(to give assent; consent)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ak'si:d]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：ac（加强）+cede（走）→一起走→同意"},{"type":"text","text":"accede to答应"},{"type":"entry","text":"repugnant","headword":"repugnant"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj.令人厌恶的(strong distaste or aversion)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rr'pAgnant]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：re（再）+pugn(打斗）+ant→总是打斗→令人厌恶的"},{"type":"text","text":"berepugnant to sb.使某人嫌恶，使某人反感"},{"type":"entry","text":"claustrophobic","headword":"claustrophobic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.（患）幽闭恐怖症的，导致幽闭恐怖症的（affected with orinclined to"},{"type":"text","text":"[,klo:stra'faubrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"claustrophobia)"},{"type":"entry","text":"subservient","headword":"subservient"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.次要的，从属的（useful in an inferior capacity)：恭顺的（obsequiously"},{"type":"text","text":"[sab'ss:rviant]"},{"type":"text","text":"submissive)"},{"type":"entry","text":"austere","headword":"austere"},{"type":"definition","text":"adji. 素的(very plain; lacking ornament)"},{"type":"text","text":"[5:'str]"},{"type":"text","text":"园源自古希腊语austeros“苦涩的”，尤指水果、葡萄酒等“使口干舌燥的”，进"},{"type":"text","text":"入英语后用来指人在举止或态度上“严厉的、朴素的”，强调缺乏热情、趣味或情"},{"type":"text","text":"感等吸引人的品质。"},{"type":"entry","text":"infectious","headword":"infectious"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.传染的，有传染性的(capable of causing infection; communicable by"}]},{"number":68,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 05 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"stringent","headword":"stringent"},{"type":"text","text":"adj(规定）严格的，苛刻的(severe);缺钱的(marked by scarcity of money, credit"},{"type":"text","text":"['strindzant]"},{"type":"text","text":"restrictions, or other financial strain)"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：string（线，绳）+ent→像用绳限制住一样→严格的"},{"type":"text","text":"These regulations are so stringenrthat we feel we have"},{"type":"text","text":"lost all our privileges."},{"type":"text","text":"划价处"},{"type":"text","text":"draconian, rigorous"},{"type":"text","text":"stringency（n.财政紧缩）"},{"type":"entry","text":"prescription","headword":"prescription"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 规定(something prescribed as a rule)"},{"type":"text","text":"[prr'skripfn]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pre（预先）+script（写）+ion→预先写好要求→"},{"type":"text","text":"prescription"},{"type":"text","text":"规定"},{"type":"text","text":"convention, regulation"},{"type":"entry","text":"shrill","headword":"shrill"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 尖叫l(scream) adj. 束耳的(high-pitched and piercing in tone or sound)"},{"type":"text","text":"[rxl]"},{"type":"entry","text":"forerunner","headword":"forerunner"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 先行者(one that announces or indicates the later arrival of another) ; 预k(a"},{"type":"text","text":"[fo:rAnar]"},{"type":"text","text":"warning sign or symptom)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：fore（前面）+runner（奔跑者）→跑在前面的人→先行者"},{"type":"text","text":"precursor"},{"type":"entry","text":"heft","headword":"heft"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.重量(weight)"},{"type":"text","text":"[heft]"},{"type":"text","text":"the spacecrafts considerable heft 宇宙飞船的巨大重量"},{"type":"text","text":"hefty（adj.很大的：超出一般的；可观的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"sleek","headword":"sleek"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 光消的, 光亮的(smooth and glossy as if polished)"},{"type":"text","text":"[sli:k]"},{"type":"entry","text":"ethnocentric","headword":"ethnocentric"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj民族优越感的：民族中心主义的（characterized by or based on the attitude"},{"type":"text","text":"[efnau'sentrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"that one's own group is superior)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ethno（种族）+centr（中心）+ic（的）→民族中心主义的"},{"type":"text","text":"ethnocentric belief民族中心主义的信念"},{"type":"entry","text":"methodology","headword":"methodology"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 方法论(a body of methods, rules, and postulates employed by a discipline)"},{"type":"text","text":"[meBa'da:lad3i]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：method（方法）+ology（学说）→方法论"},{"type":"entry","text":"wherewithal","headword":"wherewithal"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.（做某事的)所需资金(the necessary means,especially financial means)"},{"type":"text","text":"['werwrdo:1]"},{"type":"entry","text":"displace","headword":"displace"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 取代(to take the place of someone/something)：追使离开家圆(to force people"},{"type":"text","text":"[dis'plers]"},{"type":"text","text":"to move away from their home to another place)"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：dis（除去，剥夺）+place（位置）→被夺去位置→取代"},{"type":"text","text":"obviate"},{"type":"entry","text":"gentility","headword":"gentility"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.文雅，彬彬有礼（decorum of conduct）：高贵的身份（the condlition of belonging"},{"type":"text","text":"[dzen'trlati]"},{"type":"text","text":"to the gentry)"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：genti(看作gentle，温和的）+ity→彬彬有礼"},{"type":"entry","text":"inconclusive","headword":"inconclusive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 非决定性的; 无定论的(leading to no conclusion or definite result)"},{"type":"text","text":"[Inkan'klu:sIv]"},{"type":"text","text":"Given the inconclusive state of the published evidence, we do not argue here"},{"type":"text","text":"that exposure to low-level microwave energy is either hazardous or safe."}]},{"number":69,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"frivolous","headword":"frivolous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.轻薄的，轻佛的(marked by unbecoming levity)"},{"type":"text","text":"['frivalas]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：friv（愚囊）+olous→愚囊的→轻桃的"},{"type":"entry","text":"didactic","headword":"didactic"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj. 教海的 (morally instructive);说教的(boringly pedantic or moralistic)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dar'daektik]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：did（做）+act（行动）+ic→教人如何做或行动→教诲的"},{"type":"text","text":"didacticism (n.说教)"},{"type":"entry","text":"equivalent","headword":"equivalent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 相等的，等值的(equal in quantity, value, meaning."},{"type":"text","text":"equivalent"},{"type":"text","text":"[r'kwivalant]"},{"type":"text","text":"etc.)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：equi（平等的）+val(力量）+ent→力量平等的"},{"type":"text","text":"相等的"},{"type":"text","text":"be equivalent to与相等或等值"},{"type":"entry","text":"voluble","headword":"voluble"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.健谈的（talkative）：易旋转的（rotating）"},{"type":"text","text":"[va:ljabl]"},{"type":"text","text":"volubility （n.口若悬河）"},{"type":"entry","text":"transitory","headword":"transitory"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 短暂的(transient)"},{"type":"text","text":"['traensato:ri]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：trans（改变）+it（走）+ory→走过就变的→短暂的"},{"type":"entry","text":"propriety","headword":"propriety"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.礼节（decorum);适当，得体(appropriateness)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pra'prarati]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：propri恰当的）+ety→举止恰当→礼节：得体"},{"type":"entry","text":"eminent","headword":"eminent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj显赫的，杰出的(prominent, conspicuous)"},{"type":"text","text":"[eminant]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：e（向外）+min（突出）+ent→突出来→显恭的"},{"type":"text","text":"The eminent ambassador was but an indifferent linguist; yet he insisted"},{"type":"text","text":"on speaking to foreign dignitaries in their own tongues without resorting to a"},{"type":"text","text":"translator’s aid."},{"type":"entry","text":"pedant","headword":"pedant"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.迁腐之人，学究(one who unduly emphasizes minutiae in the use of"},{"type":"text","text":"['pednt]"},{"type":"text","text":"knowiedge)"},{"type":"text","text":"圈词根记忆：ped（教育）+ant→与儿童教育相关的人→学究"},{"type":"entry","text":"interchangeable","headword":"interchangeable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 可互换的(incapable of being interchanged)"},{"type":"text","text":"[intar'tfernd3abl]"},{"type":"text","text":"来自interchange（v互换）"},{"type":"text","text":"interchangeably (acv:可互换地)"},{"type":"entry","text":"corroborate","headword":"corroborate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 支持或证实(to bolster; make more certain);强化(to strengthen)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ka'ra:barert]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：cor（加强）+robor（力量）+ate→加强力量→强化"},{"type":"text","text":"corroboration（n.证实，支持）"},{"type":"entry","text":"apathetic","headword":"apathetic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 无感情的 (having or showing litle or no feeling or emotion); 无兴趣的(having"},{"type":"text","text":"[epa’θetik]"},{"type":"text","text":"little or no interest or concern)"},{"type":"text","text":"be apathetic about 对--冷淡"},{"type":"entry","text":"approbate","headword":"approbate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v 认可(to accept as valid)"},{"type":"text","text":"[eprabert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ap（加强）+prob（证明）+ate→一再证明（可行）→批准"},{"type":"text","text":"approbatory（adj.认可的；赞赏的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"predate","headword":"predate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 早于 (to precede in time; antedate)"},{"type":"text","text":"Lpri:'dert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pre（在前，早于）+date(日期）→早于"},{"type":"text","text":"antedate, precede"},{"type":"entry","text":"upshot","headword":"upshot"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.最后结果，结局(the final result)"}]},{"number":70,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 05 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"politic","headword":"politic"},{"type":"text","text":"adlj. 明智的(showing sound or pragmatic judgment)"},{"type":"text","text":"['pa:latk]"},{"type":"text","text":"advisable, desirable, prudent, judicious"},{"type":"entry","text":"versatility","headword":"versatility"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 多功能性(the quality of having many different uses)"},{"type":"text","text":"[v3:rsa'trlati]"},{"type":"text","text":"图来自versatile （adj用途广泛的）"},{"type":"text","text":"The circumstances under which phase transitions occur would limit the"},{"type":"text","text":"versatiity of latent heat as a storage method."},{"type":"definition","text":"n.问题，障碍（a difficulty or obstacle)"},{"type":"entry","text":"snag","headword":"snag"},{"type":"text","text":"[snaeg]"},{"type":"text","text":"One snag is that so far, Web services have turned out to be much harder to"},{"type":"text","text":"deliver than their champions had hoped."},{"type":"entry","text":"hitch","headword":"hitch"},{"type":"entry","text":"quadrant","headword":"quadrant"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 四分之—圆（one fourth of the circumference of a circle)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kwa:drant]"},{"type":"text","text":"国词根记忆：quadr（四）+ant→由四个部分组成→四分之一圆"},{"type":"entry","text":"hoarder","headword":"hoarder"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 围积者(a person who collects and keeps large"},{"type":"text","text":"[ho:rdar]"},{"type":"text","text":"amounts of food, money, etc., often secretly)"},{"type":"text","text":"园来自hoard（v.贮藏）"},{"type":"entry","text":"flippancy","headword":"flippancy"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.轻率，无礼(a lack of seriousness often at an improper time)"},{"type":"text","text":"['flxpansi]"},{"type":"entry","text":"peculiarity","headword":"peculiarity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 特ii{a notable or distinctive feature or characteristic)"},{"type":"text","text":"[pr,kju:li'aerati]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：peculi（ar)（特殊的）+arity→特征"},{"type":"text","text":"atribute, criterion, diagnostic, differentia, hallmark, particularity"},{"type":"entry","text":"warble","headword":"warble"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.（尤指用额音高声）唱（to sing with trills,runs,or quavers)"},{"type":"text","text":"[wo:rbl]"},{"type":"entry","text":"clique","headword":"clique"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 小集团， 小圈子(a narrow exclusive circle or group of persons)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kli:k]"},{"type":"text","text":"cliquish (adj 小集团的)"},{"type":"entry","text":"hypercritical","headword":"hypercritical"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj吹毛求疵的（excessively critical; captious)"},{"type":"text","text":"[hipa'krrtrkl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：hyper（超过）+cri（批评，判断）+ical→批评过头→欧毛求疵的"},{"type":"entry","text":"predation","headword":"predation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 捕食, 捕猫行为(the act of an animal killing and eating other animals)"},{"type":"text","text":"[prr'der{n]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：pred（抓，拿）+ation→捕食"},{"type":"entry","text":"unproductive","headword":"unproductive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj产量少的(not producing very much)：效果不佳的（not producing good"},{"type":"text","text":"results)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,Anpra'daktiv]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：un（没有）+pro（前，向前）+duct（带来）+ive（…·的）→没有成果的→产量"},{"type":"text","text":"少的"}]},{"number":71,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"text","text":"In science education, it is important to differentiate between inaccurate ideas"},{"type":"text","text":"that are conceptually unproductive and understandings that are inaccurate, and"},{"type":"text","text":"yet can foster learning of more sophisticated understandings."},{"type":"text","text":"barren"},{"type":"entry","text":"equanimity","headword":"equanimity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.沉着, 冷静 (evenness of mind especially under stress)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ekwa'nimati]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：equ（平等）+anim（心神）+ity→冷静"},{"type":"entry","text":"gigantic","headword":"gigantic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.巨大的(extremely large)"},{"type":"text","text":"[dsar'gaentrk]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：和giant（n.巨人）一起记"},{"type":"entry","text":"pessimistic","headword":"pessimistic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 悲观的(a tendency to stress the negative or unfavorable or to take the"},{"type":"text","text":"[pesr'mrstik]"},{"type":"text","text":"gloomiest possible view)"},{"type":"text","text":"bearish, defeatist, despairing, downbeat"},{"type":"entry","text":"countermand","headword":"countermand"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.取消，撤销(to cancel an order that has been given)"},{"type":"text","text":"['kauntarmend]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：counter（相反）+mand（命令）→反命令→撒销"},{"type":"text","text":"annul"},{"type":"entry","text":"hack","headword":"hack"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 非法侵入(to gain illegal access to); 砍，劈(to cut or chop with repeated and"},{"type":"text","text":"[haek]"},{"type":"text","text":"irregular blows)"},{"type":"entry","text":"tectonic","headword":"tectonic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adji. 地壳构造的(relating to the structure of the Earth’s surface or crust)"},{"type":"text","text":"[tek'ta:nrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"tectonics（n.构造地质学）"},{"type":"entry","text":"clamorous","headword":"clamorous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj 喧的 (talking loudlly or shouting)"},{"type":"text","text":"['klaemaras]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：clam（呼喊，叫喊）+or+ous（多的）→多喊叫的→喧的"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 雇佣兵 (a professional soldier hired for service in a foreign army)"},{"type":"entry","text":"mercenary","headword":"mercenary"},{"type":"text","text":"[m3:rsaneri]"},{"type":"text","text":"hack"},{"type":"entry","text":"evangelist","headword":"evangelist"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 布道者(activist; missionary);热情的推动者(an enthusiastic advocate)"},{"type":"text","text":"[tr'vaend3alrst]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：ev+angel（天使）+ist（人）→像天使一样布道的人→布道者"},{"type":"entry","text":"reconstitute","headword":"reconstitute"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 重新设立 (to provide with a new structure)"},{"type":"text","text":"[,ri:'ka:nstrtu:t]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：re（再，重新）+constitute（建立）→重新设立"},{"type":"text","text":"reconstruct, reorder, reshuffle, retool"},{"type":"entry","text":"snapshot","headword":"snapshot"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.快照(a photograph)"},{"type":"text","text":"['snaepfa:t]"},{"type":"text","text":"图组合词：snap（抓拍）+shot(照片）→抓拍照片→快照"}]},{"number":72,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 05 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"levity","