ck, shirk"},{"type":"entry","text":"grapple","headword":"grapple"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 努力设法解决(to try hard to find a solution to a problem)"},{"type":"text","text":"['graepl]"},{"type":"text","text":"grapple with 努力应对"},{"type":"entry","text":"layperson","headword":"layperson"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.门外汉(one who is a nonprofessional in a given field)：非神职人员(one who is"},{"type":"text","text":"['lerps:rsn]"},{"type":"text","text":"not a cleric)"},{"type":"text","text":"园组合词：lay(外行的）+person(人)→门外汉"},{"type":"text","text":"non-specialist"},{"type":"entry","text":"prophetic","headword":"prophetic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.先知的，预言的，预示的(correctly telling of things that will happen in the"},{"type":"text","text":"[pra'fetrk]"},{"type":"text","text":"future)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：pro（提前）+phe（说）+tic→提前说出来→先知的，预言的"},{"type":"entry","text":"insatiable","headword":"insatiable"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.不知足的，贪得无厌的(very greedy)"},{"type":"text","text":"[1n’ser[abl]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：in（不）+sati（填满）+able→填不满的→不知足的"},{"type":"entry","text":"ornamental","headword":"ornamental"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 装饰性的(of, relating to, or serving as ornament)"},{"type":"text","text":"[o:rna'mentl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：om（装饰）+ament+al→装饰性的"},{"type":"entry","text":"trenchant","headword":"trenchant"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 犀利的，尖锐的(sharply perceptive; penetrating)"},{"type":"text","text":"['trentfant]"},{"type":"note","text":"联想记忆：trench（沟）+ant→说话像挖沟，入木三分→犀利的"},{"type":"entry","text":"prevail","headword":"prevail"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.战胜(to gain ascendancy through strength or superiority)：流行，盛行(to be"},{"type":"text","text":"[prr'verl]"},{"type":"text","text":"frequent)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：pre（在前面）+vail(看作val，力量）→在力量上胜过他人→战胜"},{"type":"text","text":"conquer, master, predominate, triumph"},{"type":"entry","text":"retain","headword":"retain"},{"type":"definition","text":"v保留，保持（to keep possessio