物的才能或现象（the faculty or"},{"type":"text","text":"serendipity"},{"type":"text","text":"[seran'dipati]"},{"type":"text","text":"phenomenon of finding valuable or agreeable things not"},{"type":"text","text":"sought for)"},{"type":"text","text":"图出自18世纪英国作家Horace（荷拉斯）的童话故事The"},{"type":"text","text":"ThreePrincesofSerendip，书中主人公具有随处发现珍"},{"type":"text","text":"宝！"},{"type":"text","text":"宝的本领。"},{"type":"text","text":"Many scientic discoveries are a matter of serencdlipily:"},{"type":"text","text":"Newton was not sitting there thinking about gravity when"},{"type":"text","text":"the apple dropped on his head."},{"type":"entry","text":"halfhearted","headword":"halfhearted"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 不认真的， 不热心的(showing little interest, enthusiasm, or heart)"},{"type":"text","text":"[haef'ha:rtrd]"},{"type":"text","text":"园组合词：half（半）+heart（心）+ed→只花一半心思的→不认真的"},{"type":"entry","text":"flout","headword":"flout"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.藏视(to mock or scoff at; show scorn or contempt for);违抗"},{"type":"text","text":"[flaut]"},{"type":"note","text":"园联想记忆：（看作fly，飞）+out（出去）→飞出去→不再服从命令→违抗"},{"type":"text","text":"fleer, gibe, jeer, jest, sneer"},{"type":"entry","text":"quixotic","headword":"quixotic"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj.不切实际的，空想的（foolishly impractical)"},{"type":"text","text":"[kwrk'sa:trk]"},{"type":"text","text":"过来自DonQuixote《堂·吉诃德》，亦作quixotical"},{"type":"entry","text":"garrulous","headword":"garrulous"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 崂叨的，多话的(loquacious, talkative)"},{"type":"text","text":"['garalas]"},{"type":"text","text":"chatty, conversational, voluble"},{"type":"text","text":"garrulity (n.崂助，饶舌)"},{"type":"entry","text":"obstruct","headword":"obstruct"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.阻塞（道路、通道等)(to block or close up by an obstacle);妨碍，阻挠（to"},{"type":"text","text":"[ab'strAkt]"},{"type":"text","text":"hinder from passage, action, or operation)"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：ob（反）+struct（建造）→反着建→阻塞"},{"type":"entry","text":"paradigm","headword":"paradigm"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 范例，示范(a typical example or archetype)"},{"type":"text","text":"['paeradarm]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：para（旁边）+digm（显示）→在一旁显示→范例，示范"}]},{"number":76,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"Word List 05 >>>"},{"type":"entry","text":"obfuscate","headword":"obfuscate"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.使困感，使迷感(to muddle,confuse,bewilder)"},{"type":"text","text":"['a:bfaskert]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ob（加强）+fusc（黑的）+ate→使变成全黑→使"},{"type":"text","text":"intrepid"},{"type":"text","text":"困惑，使迷惑"},{"type":"text","text":"obfuscation（n.混滑：模处理）"},{"type":"entry","text":"augment","headword":"augment"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.提高，增加o（to become greater;increase)"},{"type":"text","text":"[o:g'ment]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：aug（增加）+ment→提高，增加"},{"type":"text","text":"enlarge, expand, heighten, mount, wax"},{"type":"entry","text":"inhibit","headword":"inhibit"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 阻b(to prohibit from doing something):抑制Kto hold in check)"},{"type":"text","text":"[in'hrbrt]"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：in（不）+hibit（拿）→不许拿→阻止：抑制"},{"type":"text","text":"bridlle, constrain, withhold"},{"type":"entry","text":"avid","headword":"avid"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 混望的(having an intense craving) ; 热心的(eager)"},{"type":"text","text":"['avrd]"},{"type":"text","text":"be avid for 渴望"},{"type":"text","text":"avidity（n.渴望；欲望）"},{"type":"entry","text":"fervent","headword":"fervent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 炙热的(very hot) ;热情的(exhibiting or marked by great intensity of feeling)"},{"type":"text","text":"['fs:rvant]"},{"type":"entry","text":"nostalgia","headword":"nostalgia"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 思乡(the state of being homesick) ; 怀|日之情(a sentimental yearning for return"},{"type":"text","text":"[na'staeld3a]"},{"type":"text","text":"to or of some past period)"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：nost（家）+alg（痛）+ia→想家想到心痛→思乡"},{"type":"text","text":"The documentary film about high school life was so realistic and evocative"},{"type":"text","text":"that feelings of nostaigia flooded over the college-age audience."},{"type":"entry","text":"pseudonym","headword":"pseudonym"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 假名，笔名(a fictitious name, especially penname)"},{"type":"text","text":"['su:danxm]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：pseudo（假)+nym（名字）→假名"},{"type":"text","text":"圆pseudonymous （adj假名的;用笔名写的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"apprehensive","headword":"apprehensive"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 害怕的(anxious or fearful that sth. bad or unpleasant willhappen) ; 敏悟的"},{"type":"text","text":"[eprr'hensrv]"},{"type":"text","text":"(capable of apprehending or quick to do so)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：ap+prehen（看作prehend，抓住）+sive→抓住不故→（因为）害怕的"},{"type":"entry","text":"seminal","headword":"seminal"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj有创意的(creative)"},{"type":"text","text":"['seminl]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：Semin（种）+al→种子的→有创意的"},{"type":"entry","text":"truculent","headword":"truculent"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 残暴的，凶很的(feeling or displaying ferocity: cruel)"}]},{"number":77,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"<<<GRE词汇精选乱序版"},{"type":"entry","text":"contradict","headword":"contradict"},{"type":"definition","text":"v. 反驳，驳斥(to affirm the contrary of a statement, etc.)"},{"type":"text","text":"[.ka:ntra'drkt]"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：contra（反）+dict（说话，断言）→说反话→反驳"},{"type":"text","text":"contradictory（adj.反驳的，反对的，抗解的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"summary","headword":"summary"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.摘要，概要（an abstract;abridgment) adj.摘要的，简略的（converting the"},{"type":"text","text":"['sAmari]"},{"type":"text","text":"main points succinctly)"},{"type":"note","text":"图词根记忆：Sum（总和）+mary→摘要，概要"},{"type":"text","text":"epitome, recapitulation"},{"type":"entry","text":"banal","headword":"banal"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj. 乏味的, 陈腐的(dullor stale; commonplace; insipid)"},{"type":"text","text":"[ba'na:l]"},{"type":"note","text":"图联想记忆：ban（禁止）+al→应该禁止的→陈腐的"},{"type":"text","text":"bland, flat, sapless, vapid"},{"type":"entry","text":"forestall","headword":"forestall"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.预先阻止，先发制人（to hinder by doing sth.ahead of time;prevent)"},{"type":"text","text":"[fo:r'st:]"},{"type":"text","text":"图组合词：fore（前面）+stall（停止）→预先阻止"},{"type":"text","text":"deter, forfend, obviate, preclude"},{"type":"entry","text":"inimical","headword":"inimical"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj敌意的，不友善的（hostile，unfriendly)"},{"type":"text","text":"[1'nimikl]"},{"type":"note","text":"圆词根记忆：in（不）+im（爱）+ical→不爱的→敌意的，不友善的"},{"type":"entry","text":"exacting","headword":"exacting"},{"type":"definition","text":"adj需要付出很大努力的：要求严格的（making severe demands;requiring great"},{"type":"text","text":"[ng'zaektin]"},{"type":"text","text":"care, effort, or attention)"},{"type":"note","text":"词根记忆：ex（表加强）+act（做）+ing（的）→努力做的→需要付出很大努力的"},{"type":"text","text":"rigorous, demanding"},{"type":"entry","text":"aridity","headword":"aridity"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 干旱(excessively dry)"},{"type":"text","text":"[a'rrdati]"},{"type":"note","text":"园词根记忆：ar（干的）+id（有性质的）+ity（表名词）→干旱"}]}]}